Subject: hpsa: Update the controller names
Git-commit: 27fb8137299d4b0ee1d248d369e8c7a1dccf54dc (partial)
Patch-mainline: v4.0-rc1
References: bnc#886292


HP expects to release several new controller cards shortly before SLES12 final
release.  We would appreciate it if the in-box driver had the appropriate name
strings for the new cards.
This patch makes no functional changes -- only the strings associated with
existing entries in the table are modified, no table entries are added,
deleted, or modified in any other way which would affect the operation of the
driver.


